<section id="about">
	<%= image_tag 'logo.svg', class: 'map-logo', alt: "GeoBITs Logo" %>
	<div class="para">
		BIT campus map is an online map covering all the places and classes in Bannari Amman Institute of Technology. The idea was to help new students to get familiar with college campus and provide an overview of which department is where. The map have two layers, SVG and satellite, and four different zoom levels, you can double tap to zoom in the map. Press or hold at any place in the map to pin point that location and share it with the url. Searching functionality in the map can help the students to find the exam halls and venues of their special classes. Hope it helps to navigate the campus and saves your time.
	</div>
	<a href='<%= root_path %>'><button class="visit-btn bigger">Explore the Campus!</button></a>
</section>

